{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "暮色中，楚留香与胡铁花在虎丘山巅遇昔日剑术名家\"摘星羽士\"帅一帆。帅一帆受李观鱼之恩所托，在此等候楚留香，以碧如秋水的长剑相逼。楚留香以柔枝为兵器，运用以柔克刚之策，先以树叶诱发帅一帆剑气，趁其剑气爆发后露出空隙，以树枝轻点其头顶，一招取胜。帅一帆虽败犹傲，投剑入池，叹服楚留香胜而不骄。离去前透露李观鱼曾对其有恩，信符所至虽死不辞。楚留香感叹此等英雄江湖已少，同时困惑李观鱼为何要杀自己。最后楚留香向胡铁花详解破剑气之法，并评价帅一帆若将剑气融入剑招则无敌于天下，但其境界仍不及石观音。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "老先生昔年莫非也是在此间烹茶品剑的盛会中人么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，只可惜故人们多已仙去，只剩下老朽百病之身，还在人间流浪，再想找一个能伴我在此烹茶试剑的人，亦不可得了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "不知老先生尊姓大名?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "老朽帅一帆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "莫非是昔年一剑动三山，力斩过天星的'摘星羽士'帅老前辈?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香果然不凡，老朽新茶初沸，阁下何不进来共饮一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "烹茶在下奉陪，若要试剑么，在下却……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "却怎么?老朽人虽已老，剑却还未老哩!",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "自然是好剑。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老夫此剑已有十三年未曾离鞘，今日为你而出，你也可以引以为傲了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "名剑出鞘，例不空回，前辈今日莫非定要取在下项上人头么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我辈武夫，正当死在剑下，你难道还怕死不成?",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "前辈若要赐教，在下也只有奉陪，但却要请教前辈一件事，以前辈的声望，想必不致隐瞒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下与前辈素无怨仇，前辈却定要取在下性命，莫非是受人所托?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，但对手若非楚留香，老夫还不屑动手。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下若还要问前辈是受谁所托，前辈想必也不肯说的，只不过前辈纵然不说，在下也能猜得出七八分。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "很好，拔出你的兵刃来动手吧!",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "遵命。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "前辈请。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这就是你的兵器?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好轻狂的少年人，纵是李观鱼，也不敢对老夫如此轻慢无礼!",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下毫无不敬之意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你这是什么意思?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "只要运用得当，大地万物，莫不是伤人的利器，若是运用不当，纵是上古神兵，也难伤人毫发，前辈高人，怎会不解此意?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "前辈剑法精妙，实为在下生平仅见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "很好，很好，很好……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下取巧，虽侥幸逃脱前辈剑下，但也未能取胜，前辈何苦……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不必说了!",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "前辈风范，果然不同……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "前辈还有吩咐?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "胜而不骄，谦恭有礼，后辈如你，又岂是前辈能及?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "多承前辈赞许，在下却不敢言胜。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你和李观鱼究竟有何仇恨?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下与李老前辈素昧平生，仇恨两字，更是无从说起。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既是如此，李观鱼为何要杀你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下不知道，李老前辈难道也未曾说起么?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "李观鱼昔年曾有恩于我，只要他信符所至，纵然要我割下自己头颅，我也在所不辞，你明白么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "text": "在下明白。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "帅一帆",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "很好，很好，很好……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人果然不愧为英雄，只可惜这样的人，在江湖中已经越来越少了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他最后的一句话，究竟有什么含意?你真的明白了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他这是在告诉我，他为了要报李观鱼之恩，就算要他性命也在所不惜，所以他虽然并不知道李观鱼为何要杀我，还是来动手了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如此说来，他真是受李观鱼所托而来的了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但李观鱼究竟为何要杀你呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "一个老人为了他的子媳，是什么事都做得出的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你方才是怎么样胜他的?我非但没看出来，连想都想不出。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "此人剑法实已登峰造极，已将有形之剑，化为无形之气，我全身都已被他笼罩，几乎连气都已透不出。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "连我都透不过气来了，何况你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我若不先设法冲出他的剑气，就只有任凭他宰割，所以我也只有冒一冒险了，乘他换气时，忽然跃起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你总该知道，对付帅一帆这样的高手，这不但是在冒险，简直和送死差不多。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是呀!这种凌空飞击的招数，只有在以强搏弱时才能用的，因为只要一击不中，就要自陷绝境，所以我看你使出这种招式来，也吓了一跳。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我身形凌空后，更看出他剑气凝练，实是无懈可击，所以我只有先以树枝上的叶子，来诱发他的剑气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这道理我就不懂了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那时他剑气已完全发挥，正如弓已引满，箭在弦上，只要轻轻一触，弦上的箭便不得不发。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我所用的就是这道理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么道理?我还是不懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我将树叶以内力逼出，触及他的剑气，他剑气本已饱涨，只要被外物触及，就立刻要发作。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "剑气一发，便不可收拾，非但那几片树叶要被完全毁灭，就是整个一个人，只怕也要被辗得粉碎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好厉害。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "但剑气被引发后，就有了空隙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为他力量已集中在那几点上，别的地方自然就难免要露出空隙，所以我就乘隙以树枝在他头上轻轻一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "但饶是如此，我还是被那剑气反激过来，震得飞了出去。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是无论如何，你还是一招就胜了他。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这一招看来虽轻松，其实却比千万招还要艰苦，何况，我那树枝虽点着了他，却绝对无法伤得了他，他本来不必认输的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如此说来，他那时若不认输，再乘势追击，你岂非就完蛋了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那倒也未必。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么又未必了呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "只因我这一着，已将他剑气破去，他若想再将剑气凝练，我也不会给他机会了，所以他若再追击，只有凭招式和我动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎知他招式就胜不了你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "若论招式之精，普天之下，只怕至今还无一人能胜得过石观音的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "若要帅一帆和石观音交手呢?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "石观音必胜无疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "何以见得?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为帅一帆还是未能将剑气练得出神入化，收放自如，也未能将剑气融入剑的招式变化中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他若能将剑气融入剑招中呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那就无敌于天下了!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    }
  ],
